overview: The user wanted to improve the aesthetics of their sleep questionnaire
  app, which they felt was functional but lacked visual appeal. The agent began
  with a thorough review of the app's styling, identifying a generic color
  palette, plain backgrounds, dense form sections, and a lack of visual
  personality. The approach involved implementing a new, calming sleep-themed
  color palette with deep indigo/purple and teal accents. Key decisions included
  redesigning the QuestionnaireForm layout, enhancing the IntroSection with
  feature cards and improved alerts, and polishing individual UI components like
  CheckboxField, RadioGroupField, Progress, and Slider. The DaytimeSection and
  ReportSection were also updated with better visual grouping and consistent
  card styling. The outcome is a more sophisticated, engaging, and aesthetically
  pleasing application that better reflects a sleep health theme.
